(How the Score Is Calculated) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Formula: Priority = min\(100, 10 + ?\(active factor weights\)\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Every job starts with a base score of 10. Then each active factor adds its weight. The) Tj
T*
(total is capped at 100.) Tj
T*
() Tj
