T*
T*
(1. Advisor creates the estimate) Tj
T*
(2. Advisor clicks "Send Approval" ? system generates a unique approval link) Tj
T*
(3. Link is sent to the customer \(via WhatsApp, SMS, or email\)) Tj
T*
(4. Customer opens the portal and sees:) Tj
T*
(   - Job and vehicle summary) Tj
T*
(   - Inspection findings \(grouped by severity: red ? amber ? green\)) Tj
T*
(   - Estimate lines with approve/decline/defer buttons) Tj
T*
(   - Job photos) Tj
T*
(5. Customer makes decisions per line) Tj
T*
(6. System records decisions and:) Tj
T*
(   - Approved lines ? proceed with work) Tj
T*
(   - Declined/deferred lines ? create Deferred Work records) Tj
T*
(   - If all lines approved ? job auto-moves to Approved) Tj
T*
(7. Advisor receives notification of customer decision) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Approval Links) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Links are hashed \(SHA-256\) for security ? raw tokens are never stored) Tj
T*
(- Links expire after 7 days by default) Tj
T*
(- Links are single-use ? once the customer submits, the link is invalid) Tj
T*
(- Links can be revoked manually by the advisor) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
