T*
(| RAM | 4 GB |) Tj
T*
(| Disk | 40 GB SSD |) Tj
T*
(| Docker | 20.10+ with Compose V2 |) Tj
T*
(| Domain | A registered domain with DNS access |) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Deployment Steps) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Clone the repository) Tj
T*
(   bash) Tj
T*
(   git clone https://github.com/hmelshenawy/superflow-api.git) Tj
T*
(   cd superflow-api) Tj
T*
(   git checkout dev) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2. Configure environment) Tj
T*
(   bash) Tj
T*
(   cp .env.example .env.production) Tj
T*
(   # Edit .env.production with your settings) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3. Build and start) Tj
T*
(   bash) Tj
T*
(   docker compose --env-file .env.production up -d) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4. Set up TLS) Tj
T*
(   - Traefik automatically provisions Let's Encrypt certificates) Tj
T*
(   - Point your domain DNS to the server IP) Tj
T*
(   - Traefik handles HTTP ? HTTPS redirect) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5. Create admin user) Tj
T*
(   - First user through the setup flow becomes admin) Tj
T*
(   - Or seed via database) Tj
T*
