(| CORS_ORIGINS | Allowed frontend origins |) Tj
T*
(| APP_DOMAIN | Your domain \(e.g., prioraflow.com\) |) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Updating) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(git pull origin dev) Tj
T*
(docker compose --env-file .env.production build) Tj
T*
(docker compose --env-file .env.production up -d) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Backups) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Database: Use mysqldump or MariaDB backup tools) Tj
T*
(- Media: Sync MinIO data directory) Tj
T*
(- Config: .env.production file should be securely stored) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(22. Security Model) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Authentication) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Staff login: JWT access tokens \(short-lived\) + Refresh tokens \(long-lived\)) Tj
T*
(- Refresh tokens: Stored as SHA-256 hashes, rotated on each use) Tj
T*
(- Rate limiting: Login \(5/min\), Refresh \(10/min\)) Tj
T*
(- Session management: View active sessions, revoke individually or all) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Customer Portal) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Token-based access: Unique hashed token per approval link) Tj
T*
(- No JWT required: Customer accesses via secure link only) Tj
T*
(- Token expiry: 7 days default) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
