stream
BT
/F1 11 Tf
16 TL
50 800 Td
(PrioraFlow Owner Manual - Page 31 of 31) Tj
T*
T*
(- Single use: Token invalidated after decision submission) Tj
T*
(- Media proxy: Customer never accesses internal storage directly) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Data Protection) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Soft deletes: Media and some records use soft deletion \(recoverable\)) Tj
T*
(- Audit logging: All significant actions are logged) Tj
T*
(- Input validation: Strict DTO validation rejects unknown fields) Tj
T*
(- CORS: Configured origins only) Tj
T*
(- Helmet: Security headers enabled) Tj
T*
(- Throttling: Global rate limiting on all API routes) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(23. Glossary) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(| Term | Definition |) Tj
T*
(|---|---|) Tj
T*
(| Job / RO | A repair order ? the main unit of work in PrioraFlow |) Tj
T*
(| Priority Score | 0?100 number indicating how urgently a job needs attention |) Tj
T*
(| Priority Level | Low / Normal / High / Critical ? derived from the score |) Tj
T*
(| Workshop Stage | The physical stage of the vehicle inside the workshop |) Tj
T*
(| Parts Status | The supply chain state for parts needed by the job |) Tj
T*
(| Customer Informed | Flag indicating the customer has been told their vehicle is ready) Tj
T*
(|) Tj
T*
(| Next Best Action | The system's recommendation for what the advisor should do next |) Tj
T*
(| Deferred Work | Estimate items the customer didn't approve ? tracked for follow-up |) Tj
T*
(| Approval Token | A secure, hashed link sent to the customer for estimate approval |) Tj
T*
(| Inspection | A structured vehicle check performed by the technician |) Tj
T*
(| Estimate | The quote/price breakdown sent to the customer |) Tj
T*
(| DMS | Dealer Management System ? the workshop's core business system |) Tj
T*
(| Promised Date | The date/time the customer was told their vehicle would be ready |) Tj
T*
(| Idle Time | How long since the job was last updated |) Tj
T*
(| Kanban Board | Visual job board organized by status columns |) Tj
T*
(| Traefik | The reverse proxy that handles routing and TLS |) Tj
T*
(| MinIO | S3-compatible object storage for media files |) Tj
T*
(| BullMQ | Background job queue powered by Redis |) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(*PrioraFlow ? Know what's urgent. Know what to do next.*) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
